C) QA & Balance Guardrails (quick reference)

Duels (same tier): 8–14s TTK target bands.

Energy sustain: baseline builds ≥8–10s continuous fire + maneuver; Advanced +15–25%.

Mobility ladder: Strike > Escort > Line > Capital.

Sensors ladder: Larger hulls trend to higher DRADIS; Visual increases only modestly.

FTL: Bigger hulls tend to longer Range and higher Cost; Command frames may have transponder discounts.

Slot identity: Enforce role signatures (Interceptor=Engine, Assault=Hull, Command=Computer) on base & Advanced.
